{"tid":1988314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約州長指，對中國封關是正確的事，但卻留低了後門讓疫情從歐洲傳入。","createTime":"2020-04-25T06:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T12:17:47.000Z","uid":78519,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"98f0dffe139b62d7ef9f5d9325897aec3ad09413","tid":1988314,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】美國紐約州州長科莫回顧疫情爆發時指，對中國封關是正確的事，但卻留低了後門讓疫情從歐洲傳入。<br />\n<br />\n科莫說：「我們關了前門，回看對中國封關做對了，但卻留下了後門敞開。所以教訓是甚麼？任何地方爆發疫症即所有地方爆發。當你看到11月及12月在中國爆發時，便要假設明天傳到美國。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/23816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F23816&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=7bb09ae9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F23816&h=d7bd53b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/23816</a>"},{"pid":"39d605d59c044aaa4a3331572dfed83c7d583540","tid":1988314,"uid":194326,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"同澳洲一樣<br />\n中國爆就禁中國<br />\n但係大學就教班老細走後門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431b2e8306dfd8acd7f72c861b9c69b2eb26dc88","tid":1988314,"uid":40267,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"你自己咪一樣叫人出門唔撚洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要死成兩萬人先叫人帶罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完左好躝啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e37176310b284d7dc6a4c3da9e61488316d2e53","tid":1988314,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"這是事實"},{"pid":"d182b460bb80d62927624437b862ade864ea1a57","tid":1988314,"uid":19728,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2